g.text: Graham is currently looking for some physical activities after work. He recently started a new ofﬁce job and sits
at a desk all day. Ideally he is looking for a place where he could swim laps in a pool, but he's willing to chose
another activity if he can ﬁnd a location that is close to work or home. He takes public transit.
Graham is heading home on the Ctrain and decides to visit calgary.ca to look for public pools. He ﬁnds an
aquatic centre in a neighbourhood close to his place and clicks the map link to ﬁnd the exact address. He wants
to know how far of a walk it is from his house, so he clicks on directions.
He is using an Android phone.
Graham needs to know approximately how long of a walk it is from his house to the aquatic centre. He plans to
check out the facilities this evening. He needs walking directions, estimated walking time, approximate distance
and possibly transit directions if he decides he want's to take the bus home.
